                     <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
                     <p>With envelope. Accompanied by a copy, in Orlando Butler Fellowes' hand, of portions of four letters: 2 from Hester Lynch Piozzi to her executors, Merton-Super Mare, 1819 Oct 18 and Penzance, 1820 Oct 10; 1 from William Augustus Conway to Sir James Fellowes, Bath, 1821 May 7; 1 from Sir James Fellowes to William Augustus Conway, York Hotel, 1821 May 8. Removed from: <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
